The latest is allowing access to KiwiSaver for farm ownership.

30
00:01:42.440 --> 00:01:46.380
A farm is a business. This is poor policy and weakens the

31
00:01:46.420 --> 00:01:49.680
fundamental purpose of KiwiSaver being a retirement scheme,

32
00:01:50.560 --> 00:01:52.840
not a general savings or business scheme.

33
00:01:53.420 --> 00:01:55.100
KiwiSaver is, of course, voluntary.

