37
00:02:08.940 --> 00:02:11.920
was permitted by a law change by a National government in

38
00:02:12.020 --> 00:02:12.940
2008.

39
00:02:13.740 --> 00:02:15.900
No subsequent government has repealed it.

40
00:02:16.660 --> 00:02:20.520
It means people have less take-home pay, and employers are

41
00:02:20.580 --> 00:02:21.360
